WEBVTT

00:00.549 --> 00:02.485
<i>Previously on Mad Men...</i>

00:02.601 --> 00:05.358
Heinz beans.
Some things never change.

00:05.459 --> 00:06.665
Oh, it's clever.

00:07.013 --> 00:08.844
We're going to lose
Jaguar unless

00:08.942 --> 00:10.296
an arrangement is made, and

00:10.375 --> 00:11.988
it involves you and her.

00:12.133 --> 00:13.708
You look radiant, Joan.

00:13.840 --> 00:17.205
You must have heard some terrible
things about me from Don Draper.

00:17.312 --> 00:18.839
Now, why would you want to
play for the other team?

00:18.974 --> 00:20.304
It's not a game.

00:20.407 --> 00:22.311
You don't get another chance
at what you have.

00:22.424 --> 00:23.976
I have it all.

